# Layout Components

This folder will contain shared layout components for your React app.

## Suggested Components

- **AppLayout.tsx**: Main layout wrapper (header, sidebar, footer, etc.).
- **Header.tsx**: Top navigation bar.
- **Sidebar.tsx**: Optional sidebar for navigation.
- **Footer.tsx**: Footer component.
- **PageContainer.tsx**: Wrapper for consistent page padding and alignment.

## Description

- Use Tailwind CSS for styling.
- Keep layout components reusable and composable.
- Provide a consistent look and feel across all pages.

